  <body>
    <segment id="1" parent="7" relname="background">Bears are not uncommon in Ontario.</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="7" relname="span">
As campers, you should be careful in the wilderness.</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="4" relname="list">
Last year several nightly attacks on campers have been reported.</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="4" relname="list">
Also, there were a number of unpleasant mountain lion encounters.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="3" relname="span">
So, it is important not to keep meat in the tent and not to sleep in the clothes worn for a barbecue.


</segment>
